snippet.title: Everyday Shooter PS3 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Everyday Shooter is a unique shooting game where every level is a "song" on an interactive album, and every action creates riffs and musical notes that add to the soundtrack.

©2008 Sony Computer Entertainment America Inc. Developed by Jonathan Mak of Queasy Games Inc.
